version_description: Tab for the demo version. This is the way I play it, is one of my favs songs and I think it's a shame they don't play it more. Hope you guys like, the strumming comes with your feelings.
This version is from original key. Other versions are transposed so i wanted to do these chords.
I believe it is played with capo on 2nd or 4th. This is an easy chord version for the 2nd fret. I am not sure about the half-acapella part in the song. The chord might be a Bm or a G. Just try.
First version of the new song.
